wlanpi-usb-ethernet (1.2.0-1) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Added keep-alive mechanism to monitor usb0 and usb1, resetting the USB
    gadget on connectivity loss to the host.
  * Implemented dynamic host IP discovery using ARP table, replacing static
    IP configuration.
  * Added ARP table refresh via broadcast ping for reliable IP discovery.
  * Enhanced logging to include discovered IPs and raw ARP output in
    /var/log/usb-ethernet-gadget.log.
  * Added net-tools dependency for ARP functionality.
  * Updated README.md with troubleshooting steps for keep-alive and IP discovery.

 -- Jerry Olla <jerryolla@gmail.com>  Sun, 22 Jun 2025 11:19:00 -0500

